  "instructions": [
    "Rinse and pick over the lentils under cold water. Drain well.",
    "In a large pot or Dutch oven, combine the lentils, onion, garlic, olive oil, crushed pineapple with its juice, cinnamon, lemon juice, salt, and pepper. Bring to a boil.",
